'''Karl Marx''' (1818-ngièn 5-ngie̍t 5-ngit —— 1883-ngièn 3-ngie̍t 14-ngit), [[Hon-sṳ]] yîm-yi̍t '''Mâ-khiet-sṳ̂''' (馬克思), he [[Tet-koet]] ke yi-chak chhut-miàng ke [[chet-ho̍k]]-kâ lâu [[sa-fi-ho̍k]]-kâ. Khì ke [[Marx chú-ngi]] he kîm-pû-ngit [[sa-fi-chú-ngi]] lâu [[khing-sán-chú-ngi]] ke lî-lun kî-chhú.

